    Verse: 5
Tags:
  - Possessions
---
People have had to make up for their spiritual impoverishment by
accumulating material things. When spiritual blessings come, material
blessings seem unimportant. ... As long as we desire material things this is
all we receive, and we remain spiritually impoverished.
